name: NFTboxHEN 02 💎📦
description:
Welcome to NFTboxHEN 📦, where we release an NFT-filled grab bag with amazing, international artists. Each edition features 1 artist in particular for the core box concept. Each box is a low-priced 1/1 edition in comparison to the value of all the NFTs inside. 

This is a one-time, NFT grab bag that, once purchased, content will be sent to the buyer and detached. Then the box is empty and becomes a cool collectible itself.

💎 EDITION 02
🎨 2 pieces by threeeyesonemind
🎨 1 piece (1/1) by PL4Y3RN0N3
🎨 1 piece (1/1) by URI HD
🎨 1 piece (1/1) by Cristina Agassini
🎨 & the box itself by Fabi Yamada
